.TH AGICTL 1 "May 2026" "ARKHE OS" "AGI Core Utilities"
.SH NAME
agictl \- Sovereign Intelligence Control Interface
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B agictl
[\fBOPTIONS\fR] \fBCOMMAND\fR [\fBARGS\fR...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBagictl\fR is the primary control interface for the ARKHE OS AGI Core.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-h, \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.TP
.B \-v, \-\-version
Show version info.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B status
Show coherence status and active nodes.
.TP
.B sync
Force temporal synchronization across OmniNet.
